title: Queen + Adam Lambert - Chicago 2014 - DVD9 Complete Multi Camera
description:
Queen + Adam Lambert - 2014/06/19 - United Center, Chicago, IL

Here is a complete Multi-Camera DVD9 I made from HD youtube rips and the audio that was recently shared here. The DVD has a few short gaps between songs but the performance is complete. Adam was the main focus of all the footage so I mixed this with plenty of wide shots to take the focus off closeups of Adam for the whole show.
